query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `weeklyBadges` (
	`id` bigint AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
	`weeklyChallenge` int NOT NULL,
	`userId` int NOT NULL,
	`rank` int NOT NULL,
	`streakLength` int NOT NULL,
	`badgeIcon` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
	`badgeName` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
	`awardedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
	`createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
	PRIMARY KEY(`id`)
);
